{"tid":1178131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3大媽變「關愛座管理員」　拍片狙擊腳傷少女︰要放上網","createTime":"2019-05-30T08:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T11:57:44.000Z","uid":51620,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc9aa873ef20d00d237dbf1bf2c197d5cf56681","tid":1178131,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"3大媽變「關愛座管理員」　拍片狙擊腳傷少女︰要放上網<br />\n<br />\n關愛座爭議無日無之。近日有腳部曾動手術的女學生搭港鐵時坐關愛座，誰料卻遇上3名自稱是「關愛座管理員」的大媽「圍剿」，更被追罵到落車？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有家長在網上討論區「親子王國」講述事件，指上周六（25日）中午12時許，其女兒與同學一同乘搭東鐵線前往紅磡。當列車駛至九龍塘站時，她女兒坐在關愛座上休息，其他同學則坐在旁邊的座位上。<br />\n<br />\n有3名年約60歲的大媽其後上車見狀，「以言語不斷詆毀，大致說現在的年輕人缺乏公民教育，不肯讓座給老人，應要再教育」。她們更自稱是「關愛座管理員」，「代表不知甚麼機構要監察現時關愛座的使用情況。」即使列車抵達終點站後，3名大媽仍繼續在月台教訓他們。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528081535474-0528_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR38QsxT-noDV-qf9Tl9EJabHP4jj1d4vaiLloMGvYjikZv78fe-QXyUkBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190528081535474-0528_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR38QsxT-noDV-qf9Tl9EJabHP4jj1d4vaiLloMGvYjikZv78fe-QXyUkBE&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1dqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=48bf699b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528081535474-0528_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR38QsxT-noDV-qf9Tl9EJabHP4jj1d4vaiLloMGvYjikZv78fe-QXyUkBE</a>"},{"pid":"c94dd9ba1e3d47f705200d29868d1c22d8e4564d","tid":1178131,"uid":136833,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"關愛座女hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c50379e8161953b33f8b7ebc5133d0b04e74a6","tid":1178131,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94dd9ba1e3d47f705200d29868d1c22d8e4564d","tid":1178131,"uid":136833,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"關愛座女hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmo